Q. I heard he has a certificate in financial advice, is this right?
  -> I'm sorry, but that information is incorrect, he has a certificate in 자격증


9번 빈출 표현

Q. Can you tell me about his work experience in detail? (문제에따라 경력중 걸러야 할것이 생길 수 있다. 특정 경력(작가)을 묻는경우)
  -> Let me see, there are three thnigs on the list    ( 옛날 직업부터 대답하기.)
    firstly, he worked as a 직급 at 회사 from 년도 to 년도 (he worked as a 직급)
    Then, he was a 직급 at 회사 from 년도 to 년도  (he was a 직급 )
    And now, he has been working as a 직급 at 회사 since 년도. ( has been working as a 직급)
    This is information you're looking for.
    (시간없으면 년도 하나 생략)

Q. Can you describe his educational background in detail?
  -> Let me see, there are two thnigs on the list    ( 옛날 학력부터 대답하기.)
      firstly he graduated from 학교 with bachelor's degree in 전공 in 년도
     After that, he got his master's degree from 학교 in 년도. his major was 전공
     This is information you're looking for.





